result.name: MouMouClub

reviews.text: my boss's favourite chicken curry shop
Hot pot. So good

Fairly good selection of different grades of beef. This is a hot pot restaurant. Separate vegetable bar. Mix of dipping sauces. Quality  and  taste is good. Service is reasonable and prices are moderate. It is okay if you are only interested in beef, but if you are interested in other meats then suggest to look at a Korean barbecue.

Great selection of all you can eat courses. Price is reasonable. There is also a small bar where you can pick other vegetables to cook, drinks are also free flow, there's also a dessert bar. Great place to eat in a group, reservation is recommended
Price is good, but there's not a large variety of food.

result.adr_address: 香港粉嶺和滿街8號
result.name: 牛涮鍋

reviews.text: 食物一般，漏單情況非常嚴重。
一係吃最平吃多D青菜，一係吃最貴日本黑毛和牛
好食，環境好
職員服務態度好， 點菜嘅嘢好快就會上， 價錢又唔貴， 款式呢就係日式嘅邊爐冇中式嘅咁多不過係正常嘅， 環境十分之好， 所以比較多人食 就會有機會排隊呢就排得比較耐
$130就有90分鐘放題，係平但係冇哈根達斯食。有雞牛豬，個人喜歡牛豬，相反牛真係一般......其他配菜冇乜掂過，所以不作評論

result.formatted_address: 8 Wo Mun St, Fanling, Hong Kong
result.name: Regentville Shopping Centre

reviews.text: Small local mall. Not visited by mainlanders with suitcases. Pleasant.
Good place to shop daily living needs,  supermarket, drug store, electrical appliance, clothing and restaurant, etc. Also have hourly carpark services.
Very good on eating,but so many sale clothes shop

Ordinary Hong Kong shopping centre. There is the supermarket (Wellcome) and the seafood restaurant as well as the usual crop of chain shops, clothes shops and mobile phones and accessories. The best thing is the direct access to the wet market.
There is nothing special, a shopping place for people living in the area.
Nice clean shopping centre. Has a lot of shops and a few places for dining from Pizza, Restaurant, Noodles and other fast food chains. Not overly crowded, easy to move around.
